    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292260/extras/be1c1bf14e7fddbda3745eecd559b7ec.poster.avif?t=1772048829\" width=624 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292260/extras/be1c1bf14e7fddbda3745eecd559b7ec.webm?t=1772048829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292260/extras/be1c1bf14e7fddbda3745eecd559b7ec.mp4?t=1772048829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Star Wars™: Dark Forces Remaster 由 Nightdive Studios 团队倾力打造，通过其专有 KEX engine 实现全面重制。无论新老玩家均可畅享 Star Wars: Dark Forces Remaster 的升级版玩法、高分辨率纹理、优化版光照与渲染效果以及对手柄操作的全面支持。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1995 年的 Star Wars: Dark Forces 原版游戏曾为第一人称射击游戏树立了标杆，为玩家提供了高度的行动自由和互动性、种类丰富的道具与强化物品，以及引人入胜的游戏环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292260/extras/1d122bcde3b6809c69086c4c244d782c.poster.avif?t=1772048829\" width=624 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292260/extras/1d122bcde3b6809c69086c4c244d782c.webm?t=1772048829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292260/extras/1d122bcde3b6809c69086c4c244d782c.mp4?t=1772048829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款首部《星球大战》第一人称射击游戏中，玩家将扮演凯尔·卡塔恩——一名叛逃银河帝国的雇佣兵。卡塔恩加入了义军同盟的秘密行动部门，奉命潜入银河帝国内部，在那里他发现了暗中进行的黑暗士兵计划。该计划旨在开发新一代帝国战斗机器人与动力装甲冲锋队，若放任其推进，银河帝国的统治将愈发不可撼动，唯有卡塔恩与义军同盟能阻止这场危机。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可进入“保险库”。保险库中精心收藏了各类开发资料和游戏内资产，彰显了这部经典之作的丰富历史。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引人入胜的第一人称地面战斗，包括十种武器和二十种类型的敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >先进的 3D 渲染技术实现了光照与氛围特效的全面升级。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以获得各种强化道具，包括生命值提升、护盾、武器和弹药。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗方式多样。在战斗中，玩家可以选择徒手格斗、爆炸地雷、热能雷管以及爆能枪和其他远程武器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含沉浸式的环境解谜与迷宫探索。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292260/extras/c54384dbc5286571cf503516ca84940b.poster.avif?t=1772048829\" width=624 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292260/extras/c54384dbc5286571cf503516ca84940b.webm?t=1772048829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292260/extras/c54384dbc5286571cf503516ca84940b.mp4?t=1772048829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
